{"type": "article", "id": 2884, "title": "Leica X「Edition Moncler」相机", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-16T07:54:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232322Q2OxHzYUwBELkpo9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t德国相机制造商 Leica 日前与法国时尚品牌 Moncler 联手，为最新推出的 Leica X  相机打造了一款联名限定版本。设计师选择在 Leica X 的复古造型轮廓上，通过 Moncler 标志性的红、白、蓝三色条纹装点机身，并且每款相机均配备了由 Moncler 特别定制的相机包，透出出浓浓的法式浪漫风情。这款相机配备了 1650 万像素的 APS-C 画幅 CMOS 传感器，并搭载了一个 35mm f/1.7 的 Summilux 23mm ASPH 定焦镜头。 Leica X「Edition Moncler」相机将于近期登陆 Leica 和 Moncler 指定门店和线上店铺。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232320Ue0hMIyj7qm6ATVP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232320VLegh3BsX0nj4WPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323213uaZGF4EdyJsBmYx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232321UFHhLfwZe1YaJysk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323210YJOjFTsfKbVmNka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}